<p><font color="#669900"><b>GIMP - The Pixel Juggler</b></font></p>
<p>GIMP has a new interface. The free image processing application has undergone substantial improvement. The new menus greatly reduce the time needed to get used to GIMP, and the new tool and object properties overview speeds up your work. If you wish, you can continue to use the old mode. GIMP offers layer technology, image conversion, macro capabilities, and lots of predefined filters and transformation effects.</p>
